{"tid":2094030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳文敏：國安法下是有罪推定  質疑唱歌舉旗何以分裂國家  提醒政府威嚇和鎮壓只會適得其反","createTime":"2020-07-04T09:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T17:54:37.000Z","uid":7542,"like":112,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"5958cb790462be45391691767722c1f2f6a182cb","tid":2094030,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:21:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>大學生涯上到陳文敏堂，可以算係最幸運嘅一件事 </strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港大法律學院公法講座教授陳文敏認為，《港區國安法》涉及不少定義模糊的權力，令執法者有空間濫權，認為不應以保護國家安全為名，合理化威權統治或任意使用權力。陳文敏在港大法律學院一個論壇上，舉出《港區國安法》多條條文，指當中的定義含糊，有可能牴觸《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》，例如列明除非法官信納被告不會繼續危害國家安全，否則不得保釋。<strong>他質疑幾乎是有罪推定，而非無罪推定，認為不應利用還柙作為懲罰。而《港區國安法》內多項字眼，例如「國家機密」、「 國家安全」及「勾始外國勢力」均沒有清晰定義。</strong><br />\n<br />\n陳文敏說，<strong>不明白為何唱歌、舉旗或叫口號可視作分裂國家</strong>，指《港區國安法》沒有明確訂明分裂國家的行為。如果示威者日後改用其他口號或字眼代替，甚至用白紙示威，當局是否亦要禁止。他說不會質疑保護國家安全的需要，<strong>認為政府贏得人民信任和尊重，正是國家安全的最佳保障，威嚇和鎮壓只會適得其反。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535789-20200704.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535789-20200704.htm&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmt5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=889aba65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535789-20200704.htm&h=16164054\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535789-20200704.htm</a>"},{"pid":"95c532139d0e7543ed621afaee73aab494e00f74","tid":2094030,"uid":7542,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:23:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>五毛開始進場恐嚇，大家可唔可以幫手撐住呢個以歷史傳播知識嘅Channel <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gwl0TLLfRcw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fgwl0TLLfRcw&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmt5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=0e2bf929\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gwl0TLLfRcw</a>"},{"pid":"1145b88e79595f904fc3f10a47fe0f959c2380a1","tid":2094030,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066ee906dc08ddb8431f21ac80e3d92f5362c3d3","tid":2094030,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1ad8fa79a04741dbf58a1472b21aa71ddc4684","tid":2094030,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbd6e5c01a055cc7f836c2a96fe8b4dc1f47ea5","tid":2094030,"uid":51271,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:34:07.000Z","msg":"甚至用白紙示威，當局是否亦要禁止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30662d1854bf659a569b77e24bb85e10f706b0e1","tid":2094030,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:36:12.000Z","msg":"「光復香港，時代革命」有罪嗎？看政府及警隊搬石頭砸自己的腳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2094007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2094007</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dafa6